9 tiam2 koe3 10 hun, toa7-hou7 toa7 kah na2-chhiunn7 u7 lang5 mi kui-pe2 chioh8-thau5-liap8-a2 teh khian thang-a2-mng5, keh-piah kam-a2-tiam3 e5 khanpang hou7 siau2-kui2-a2 hong chhoe poe--khi3, lak ti7 thou5-kha piang3 chit8-siann chiok toa7-siann, A-lian kiann kah chau2 lai5 kap goa2 che7, i che7 ti7 goa2 to3-chhiu2-peng5 hit-chiah lian2-a2-i2, khoann3 goa2 teh bo5-eng5 m7-kann2 ka7 goa2 lu5, che7 ti7 lian2-a2-i2 teng2-thau5, iong7 boe2-chui chhut-lat8 go5-lai5 go5-khi3, go5 beh 10 hun-cheng chiah kiu-kiu-a2 kong2:
“Pa5-a2, tu2-a2 a-ma2 koh kha3 tian7-oe7 lai5 neh, i kong2 u7 chiok che7 oe7 beh ka7 goa2 kong2, a-ma2 koh kong2 pa-pa teh koann2 khang-khoe3, m7-thang ka7 li2 kio3, a-ma2 kong2 Soann-a2-kha hong-hou7 chiok toa7--e5, soann-teng2 e5 chui2 chiok toa7-kang2, soa-a2, chioh8-thau5 long2 toe3 soann-teng2 e5 thou5-kou5 chhiang5--loh8-lai5, ku7-ni5 chou2-leng5 e5 chhiu7-a chai be7-hu3 toa7-chang5 to7 kap kui-phian3 soann-piah lu--loh8-lai5, toa7-se3-liap8 chioh8-thau5 ka2 cho3-hoe2, ka2 kah khih-khih-khok8-khok8, chhiu7-a2 kiann2 kap chhiu7-a-ma2 chim3 ti7 toa7-kang2 chui2 lai7-te2, chhiang5 kah pin-pin-pong7-pong7......”A-lian na2 kong2 bak8-sai2 na2 lau5, goa2 e5 tian7-pit teng3 ti7 oe7-tou5-pang tit8-tit8 it-tit8 chhoah, tian7-nau2 teng2-thau5 hit-e5 tiam2 ju2 lai5 ju2 toa7, kui-e5 Page long2 hoe--khi3.
