A-lian che7 ti7 i2-a2 teng2, kui-bin7 long2 si7 bak8-sai2 kap phinn7-chui2, be7-su ka-chiong3 phah e5 hoeh-bin7, goa2 ka7 khang-khoe3 ham7 A-lian pang3 ti7 pang5-keng lai7, sui5 kou2 tian7-oe7 tng2 Soann-a2-kha, tian7-oe7 soah be7 thong, tian7-oe7 hoan jih8--loh8, “tonn!” nng7-siann, chit8-e5 cha-bou2 sui5 kong2-oe7: “Hoa-lian te7-khu in-ui7 chhit-ho7 hong-thai-hou7 eng2-hiong2, soann3-lou7 be7 thong, bo5 hong-pian7 e5 sou2-chai7, chiah chhiann2 li2 goan5-liong7.”
A-lian ti7 pang5-keng lai7 khau3 kah khun3--khi3,  goa2 ka7 pho7-khi bin5-chhng5, poeh8-a2 ti7 pak8-tou2 kinn5 pau5 chit8-lian3, so2-si5 chah--leh, phe-chhia tng2 Soann-a2-kha.
Ti7 toa7-lou7 teng2, hong na7 sian3 chiann3-peng5 chhia to7 phiah chiann3-peng5, sian3 to3-peng5 han-tou2-luh to7 ai3 phang2 chiann3-peng5, chiah be7 sai2 jip8-khi3 kau-a2-te2, chhia-lian2 hou7 chui2 im beh chit8-poann3, bo5 seng5 teh sai2-chhia, tian-to3 seng5 teh sai2-chun5, thau3-hong sian3-hjou7, ou-am3 e5 kau2-ho7 kong-lou7 teng2-thau5, kan-tann goa2 chit8-tai5 chu7-iong7-chhia teh kap chhit-ho7 hong-thai chhia-piann3.
Soann-chui2 kam5 thou5-chioh8-soa kap chhiu7-a2-kin, ti7 beh jip8-khi3 Soann-a2-kha e5 soann-lou7 teng2 chhoah-lau5, goa2 sai2 si3-lian2 chun5-a2 tui3 soann e5 khang-chhui3 kauh--koe3-khi3, Soann-a2-kha e5 ku7-chhu3 to2 chit8-peng5 khi3, ng3 soann-piah e5 hit-tou2 piah kap toa7-chui2 chhoah-lau5 cho3-hoe2 lau5--khi3, ui3 toa7-mng5 piann3 chhut-lai5 thian5--nih.
2001 ni5 hou7 hong-thai chhoa7 toa7-hou7 chhoah-lau5, tui3 Hoa-lian hann7--koe3, ka7 soann-teng2 bo5 lang5 koan2 bo5 lang5 chhap e5 bun7-te5 long2 peng2-peng2--chhut-lai5, soann-piah phoa3-khang lau5-hoeh, kui2-na7 10 lang5 toe3 hong-thai cho3-hoe2 khi3.
